g.text: The game follows the life of Sleepy Cat -- whose main

g.text: objective in life is to just sleep. However, weird

g.text: things start happening in Sleepy Cat's neighbourhood,

g.text: Meowhattan! The river has become a weird colour,

g.text: strange men in the forests, things growing in their

text.font-family: Comic Shanns, monospace, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: friend's house. Help Sleepy Cat investigate these
